title: Temple of the Undead General
story: For centuries the temple of the Undead General was considered lost. Currently it is overrun with monkeys, indifferent to the history of the place.

notes.text: A large chest containing a looking glass of illusions.
A battered door with two keyholes on the southern wall of the large room.
A sword among rubble on the ground.
A corpse of an ogre, a key nearby.
